{% from "components/skip-link/macro.njk" import skipLink %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<p>The skip link is visually hidden until it receives keyboard focus. Press
  <kbd>Tab</kbd> when the page loads to see it appear at the top-left corner.
  Every page on this site already includes the skip link in the base layout.</p>

<p>The markup produced by the macro:</p>

<pre><code>{% raw %}{% from "components/skip-link/macro.njk" import skipLink %}
{{ skipLink() }}{% endraw %}</code></pre>

<p>Produces:</p>

<pre><code>&lt;a class="skip-link" href="#main-content"&gt;Skip to main content&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>

<h2>Custom target and text</h2>

<pre><code>{% raw %}{{ skipLink({ href: "#content", text: "Jump to content" }) }}{% endraw %}</code></pre>

<p>Inline demo (tab through to reveal):</p>

<div style="position: relative; border: 1px dashed var(--nhsuk-mid-grey); padding: var(--nhsuk-spacing-4);">
  {{ skipLink({ href: "#content", text: "Jump to content" }) }}
  <p>Tab here to see the skip link appear above.</p>
</div>
